 Nigerian born and Chicago based Gospel artist, Josh Blayze has released the song, GLORIFY which was one of the songs he wrote and performed at his last live recording concert tagged, GRATITUDE 2.0 which took place at Schaumburg Community Church. The song was produced by Chris Terry, a prolific musicologist in the Chicago land area. The post production of the project was done by P.mo and the Video was edited by Israel Mona. WATCH VIDEO  The post VIDEO: Josh Blayze – Glorify appeared first on Latest Naija Nigerian Music, Songs & Video – Notjustok. Source: Not just okay